Package fr.warzou.virtualcard.utils.property

Provides every interfaces about the Property system.

This is currently split into 2 main implementation :
  • AbstractPropertyMap give a classic PropertyMap.
  • AbstractLockablePropertyMap give a AbstractPropertyMap with the capacity to be lock.
Version:
0.0.2
Author:
Warzou
